TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT CS_POSITION.NAME as NAME, CS_POSITION.GENERICATTRIBUTE6 AS GA6, CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS EFF_ST, CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS EFF_END FROM CS_POSITION where CS_POSITION.removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: NAME = LOOKUP_AGENT AND EFF_ST <= COMPENSATION_DATE AND EFF_END > COMPENSATION_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT B.PAYEEID AS PAYEE_ID, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE3 AS B_name, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE5 AS Pay_Meth, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE6 AS LOCAL_BN, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE7 AS LOCAL_BC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE8 AS LOCAL_ACC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE9 AS USD_BN, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE10 AS USD_BC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE11 AS USD_ACC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE12 AS AUD_BN, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE13 AS AUD_BC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE14 AS AUD_ACC, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE4 AS SWIFT_CODE, A.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS STATUS_CODE FROM CS_PARTICIPANT A inner join CS_PAYEE B ON A.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('22000101','YYYYMMDD') AND a.islast =1 AND B.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('22000101','YYYYMMDD') AND b.islast =1 AND A.PAYEESEQ = B.PAYEESEQ

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ST_MANTXN.DEC_RECORD_NO, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_CMP_CD, IN_ST_MANTXN.DTE_COMPENSATION_DATE, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_ADJ_TYPE, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_AGENT_CODE, IN_ST_MANTXN.DEC_ADJ_VALUE, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_CUR_TYPE, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_SUBMITTED_BY, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_DESCRIPTION, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_EVENT_TYPE, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_EXPENSE_EARNING_CD, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_BALANCE_EARNING_CD, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_GST_EARNING_CD, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_ACCOUNT_IND, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_REASON_CD, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_FILE_NAME, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS, IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_AGYINDICATOR, CASE WHEN IN_ST_MANTXN.TXT_CUR_TYPE IN ('SGD', 'BND') THEN nvl(IN_ST_MANTXN.DEC_LOCALVALUE, IN_ST_MANTXN.DEC_ADJ_VALUE) ELSE IN_ST_MANTXN.DEC_LOCALVALUE END DEC_LOCALVALUE FROM IN_ST_MANTXN, IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'MANTXN_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.DEC_RUNNING_FLG = 1

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_EVENTTYPE.EVENTTYPEID as EVENTTYPEID FROM CS_EVENTTYPE WHERE CS_EVENTTYPE.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('22000101','YYYYMMDD')

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(CMP_CD) OR (CMP_CD != '011' AND CMP_CD != '014' AND CMP_CD != '2' AND CMP_CD != '4' AND CMP_CD != 'SG' AND CMP_CD != 'BN') , NULL,CMP_CD)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_CMP_CD
O_ADJ_VALUE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF( :LKP.LKP_POSITION_GA6(LOOKUP_AGENT,COMPENSATION_DATE)='AFA',
IIF(INSTR(EXPENSE_EARNING_CD,'||') =0, ABORT('ERROR : for FA Agent, the expense code must be “||” or pair of code separated by “||”. '||LOOKUP_AGENT), NULL),
IIF(INSTR(EXPENSE_EARNING_CD,'||') >0,ABORT('ERROR : for AGY Agent, the expense code must be not “||”. '||LOOKUP_AGENT),NULL)
)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: EXPENSE_EARNING_Check

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IS_DATE(CYCLE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD'), TO_DATE(CYCLE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD'), ABORT('ERROR : CYCLE DATE IS NOT DATE'||CYCLE_DATE))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_CYCLE_DATE
V_ORDER_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IS_DATE(TXT_KEY_VALUE,'YYYY-MM-DD'), TO_DATE(TXT_KEY_VALUE,'YYYY-MM-DD'), ABORT('ERROR : CYCLE DATE IS NOT DATE'||TXT_KEY_VALUE))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_OPER_CYCLE_DATE
V_Cheque

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(V_Cheque != 1, IIF(((//CUR_TYPE = 'SGD' OR CUR_TYPE = 'BND') AND (LOCAL_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_ACC) OR LOCAL_BN = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_BN) OR LOCAL_BC = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_BC) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ) OR ((CUR_TYPE = 'USD') AND (USD_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(USD_ACC) OR SWIFT_CODE = '' OR ISNULL(SWIFT_CODE) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ) OR ((CUR_TYPE = 'AUD') AND (AUD_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(AUD_ACC) OR SWIFT_CODE = '' OR ISNULL(SWIFT_CODE) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ), NULL,CUR_TYPE),CUR_TYPE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_CUR_TYPE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(CMP_CD) OR (CMP_CD != '011' AND CMP_CD != '014' AND CMP_CD != '2' AND CMP_CD != '4' AND CMP_CD != 'SG' AND CMP_CD != 'BN') , 'ERROR: INVAILD COMPANY CODE.Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(ADJ_TYPE) ,'ERROR: INVAILD ADJ_TYPE, PLEASE CHECK. Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(AGENT_CODE) OR AGENT_CODE ='' , 'ERROR:AGENT CODE IS NULL OR EMPTY. Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(ADJ_VALUE), 'ERROR:ADJ_VALUE IS NULL,PLEASE CHECK. Record No:'||TO_CHAR(RECORD_NO), IIF(IN(EVENT_TYPE,'Daily_Ad_Hoc_After_Tax','Daily_Ad_Hoc_Before_Tax') AND ADJ_VALUE <=0 ,'ADJ_VALUE can not less than or equal to 0 when EVENT_TYPE in (Daily_Ad_Hoc_After_Tax,Daily_Ad_Hoc_Before_Tax)','') ) ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(EVENT_TYPE) or EVENT_TYPE='' ,'ERROR: INVAILD EVENT_TYPE, PLEASE CHECK. Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| DECODE(ACCOUNT_IND , 'Y',null, '1',null, 'N',null, '0',null,'ACCOUNT_IND is invalid') ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(REASON_CD) or REASON_CD='' ,'ERROR: INVAILD REASON_CD, PLEASE CHECK. Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| IIF(IN(CMP_CD,'014','2','BN') AND TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD='C' ,'BN Country can not has check:'||RECORD_NO,'' ) ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(BU_NAME) OR BU_NAME ='', 'ERROR: CAN NOT FOUND THE BU NAME. Record No:'||RECORD_NO,'') ||'.'|| IIF(ISNULL(POS_NAME) OR POS_NAME ='', 'ERROR: CAN NOT FOUND THE POSITION NAME. Record No :'||RECORD_NO ,'') ||'.'|| iif(isnull(B_name) or B_name='','Agent ('||LOOKUP_AGENT||') do not have Beneficiary_Name in TrueComp', iif(isnull(CUR_TYPE) or CUR_TYPE='','ERROR: Cur_type is null in record: '||to_char(RECORD_NO),'')) ||'.'|| IIF(V_Cheque != 1 AND NOT ISNULL(STATUS_CODE) AND STATUS_CODE<>'70', IIF(((//CUR_TYPE = 'SGD' OR CUR_TYPE = 'BND') AND (LOCAL_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_ACC) OR LOCAL_BN = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_BN) OR LOCAL_BC = '' OR ISNULL(LOCAL_BC) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ) OR ((CUR_TYPE = 'USD') AND (USD_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(USD_ACC) OR SWIFT_CODE = '' OR ISNULL(SWIFT_CODE) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ) OR ((CUR_TYPE = 'AUD') AND (AUD_ACC = '' OR ISNULL(AUD_ACC) OR SWIFT_CODE = '' OR ISNULL(SWIFT_CODE) ) AND (POS_NAME != '' AND NOT ISNULL(POS_NAME)) ), 'Agent code('||AGENT_CODE||') does not have enought'|| CUR_TYPE||' account information ' ,''),'')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ERROR_MSG

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: //IIF( IN(EVENT_TYPE,'Daily Ad Hoc After Tax','Daily Ad Hoc Before Tax'),CUR_TYPE||'_DAH',CUR_TYPE) IIF( IN(EVENT_TYPE,'Daily_Ad_Hoc_After_Tax','Daily_Ad_Hoc_Before_Tax'),CUR_TYPE||'_DAH',CUR_TYPE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_GA5

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif( length(LEV1_CD)=8,LEV1_CD,
DECODE(CMP_CD , '011','SGT', '014','BRT', '2' ,'SGT', '4','BRT', 'SG' ,'SGT' ,'BN','BRT' ,'IWH','SGT', ABORT('INVLAID COMPANY CODE:'||CMP_CD) ) ||SUBSTR(LEV1_CD, LENGTH(LEV1_CD) - 4,5))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: LOOKUP_AGENT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_REASON.REASONID as REASONID FROM CS_REASON WHERE CS_REASON.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('22000101','YYYYMMDD')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_BUSINESSUNIT.NAME as BU_NAME, CS_POSITION.NAME AS POS_NAME, CS_POSITION.GENERICATTRIBUTE2 AS GA2 FROM CS_POSITION INNER join cs_payee on CS_POSITION.REMOVEDATE= to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and CS_POSITION.islast =1 and cs_payee.removedate =to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and cs_payee.islast =1 and CS_POSITION.payeeseq = cs_payee.payeeseq INNER join CS_BUSINESSUNIT ON CS_BUSINESSUNIT.MASK = cs_payee.BUSINESSUNITMAP AND CS_BUSINESSUNIT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ =CS_POSITION.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ
